name: @burnedbyairfryer 01. (My first digital collage piece)
description:
First post on ig: @burnedbyairfryer
First piece created after just learning photoshop & my first digital art piece ever.

After recent years of feeling lost, struggling with work and becoming numb to my previous passion of dance due to chronic pain & anxiety..I told myself on my 30th birthday that I will finally learn photoshop & finally commit to collage or digital artwork. That day came this year April 2021..This was the start of my journey into photoshop and after 100+ everydays..you can say my beginning into NFT land.

Digital art is literally all I have right now. Been dealing with social withdrawal & just stuck inside my house before we were forced to stay in the house...It's been hard. Still is, but every time I finish a piece. Whether it's "good" or "bad", I can't help, but to feel a sense of accomplishment. A feeling I haven't gotten to feel in forever. A feeling I don't seem to remember. It slowly gives me confidence again & lets me know that my thoughts & efforts exist. At this point I'm kind of rambling about my depression & everything I have been dealing with for years...but if you collect this. Just know this is really the start of everything.
